sql_query.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM "web_hooks" INNER JOIN "web_hook_event_types_hooks" ON "web_hook_event_types_hooks"."web_hook_id" = "web_hooks"."id" INNER JOIN "web_hook_event_types" ON "web_hook_event_types"."id" = "web_hook_event_types_hooks"."web_hook_event_type_id" WHERE "web_hooks"."active" = TRUE AND (web_hooks.wildcard_web_hook = TRUE OR web_hook_event_types.name = 'tag') LIMIT 1

sql_query.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "tags" INNER JOIN "category_tags" ON "tags"."id" = "category_tags"."tag_id" WHERE "category_tags"."category_id" = 206
SELECT "tags".* FROM "tags" WHERE (lower(tags.name) IN ('nope')) ORDER BY "tags"."id" ASC LIMIT 1

SELECT "categories"."name" FROM "categories" INNER JOIN "category_tags" ON "categories"."id" = "category_tags"."category_id" WHERE "category_tags"."tag_id" = 46 AND "categories"."id" IN (1, 206, 197, 198)

SELECT "categories"."name" FROM "categories" INNER JOIN "category_tag_groups" ON "category_tag_groups"."category_id" = "categories"."id" INNER JOIN "tag_groups" ON "tag_groups"."id" = "category_tag_groups"."tag_group_id" INNER JOIN "tag_group_memberships" ON "tag_group_memberships"."tag_group_id" = "tag_groups"."id" INNER JOIN "tags" ON "tags"."id" = "tag_group_memberships"."tag_id" WHERE "categories"."id" IN (1, 206, 197, 198) AND "tags"."id" = 46
